column2: select distinct title from tvprogram as t join content as c on t.content_id = c.content_id where (c.content_type = 'Movies' and kids_content = 'Y' and t.program_date >= '2020-06-01 00:00' and t.program_date < '2020-07-01 00:00')

select distinct t1.title from content as t1 join tvprogram as t2 on t1.content_id = t2.content_id where (t1.kids_content = 'Y' and t1.content_type = 'Movies' and t2.program_date >= '2020-06-01' and t2.program_date < '2020-07-01')

select distinct c.title as title from tvprogram as t join content as c on t.content_id = c.content_id where (t.program_date >= '2020-06-01' and t.program_date <= '2020-06-30' and c.kids_content = 'Y' and c.content_type = 'Movies')

select distinct title from content as c join tvprogram as t on c.content_id = t.content_id where (kids_content = 'Y' and content_type = 'Movies' and program_date >= '2020-06-01' and program_date <= '2020-06-30')

select distinct title from content as c join tvprogram as t on c.content_id = t.content_id where (program_date >= '2020-06-01' and program_date <= '2020-06-30' and kids_content = 'Y' and content_type = 'Movies')
